          <p>We've personally tested dozens of telescopes under real-world observing conditions across multiple years, evaluating performance on Moon, planets, deep sky objects, and double stars from various light pollution environments. Each recommendation below represents proven equipment delivering reliable performance for its intended purpose and price point. Whether you're complete beginner taking first steps into astronomy or experienced observer seeking specific capabilities, you'll find appropriate options matching your needs.</p>
